    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="sigmoid-or-tanh？"><a href="#sigmoid-or-tanh？" class="headerlink" title="sigmoid or tanh？"></a>sigmoid or tanh？</h1><p>Sigmoid outputs a value between 0 and 1 which makes it a very good choice for binary classification.<br>You can classify as 0 if the output is less than 0.5 and classify as 1 if the output is more than 0.5.<br>It can be done with tanh as well but it is less convenient as the output is between -1 and 1.(Sigmoid<br>输出的值介于 0 和 1 之间，这使其成为二元分类的一个非常好的选择。 如果输出小于 0.5，则可以将其归类为 0，如果输出<br>大于 0.5，则归类为 1。 它也可以用 tanh 来完成，但是它不太方便，因为输出在<br>-1 和 1 之间。)</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
